sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Registry Persistence via Service in Safe Mode
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects the modification of the registry to allow a driver or service to persist in Safe Mode.

sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Add SafeBoot Keys Via Reg Utility
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects execution of "reg.exe" commands with the "add" or "copy" flags on safe boot registry keys. Often used by attacker to allow the ransomware to work in safe mode as some security products do not
